\fB\-\-no\-pager\fR
is not given; overrides
\fI$PAGER\fR\&. Right back up in yo muthafuckin ass. Settin dis ta a empty strang or tha value
"cat"
is equivalent ta passing
\fB\-\-no\-pager\fR\&.
.RE
